# No Silent Money Mutation

Canonical source: `docs/dev/rules/no-silent-money-mutation.md`

Apply that document as the authoritative rule text.

Short form:

1. Prevent invalid money entry first.
2. Explain unavoidable adjustments inline at the moment they happen.
3. Never rewrite user-entered money as a side effect of a toggle, mode switch,
   dialog close, or state transition.
